Ubuntu Security Notices

USN-7856-1












USN-7856-1: Linux kernel (HWE) vulnerabilities








Publication date






4 November 2025










Overview






Several security issues were fixed in the Linux kernel.










Releases







 24.04 LTS













 Open side navigation





Packages



 linux-hwe-6.14 - Linux hardware enablement (HWE) kernel





Details





